跌企稳的态势。与此同时，两国关系中的消极因素也很突出。美方顽固推进遏华战略，不断采取干涉中国内政、抹黑中国形象、损害中方利益的错误言行，对此我们予以坚决反对反制。 相互尊重、和平共处、合作共赢，始终是中方看待和处理中美关系的根本原则。以和为贵、以稳为重、以信为本，是中方处理今年中美关系的遵循。对布林肯国务卿此次访问，中方主要聚焦五大目标。 全文：更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f70e91109dfbc7ce8670c8c5e77cd9c3_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653835647"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIt7PDp621sbIoEAMaCTEwNzU3NDQ2OSCoyZyxBjAAOPUCQBxyCTY1MzgzNTY0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1713875663.935513", "card_id": "Q_653433721", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你坚持使用哪款智能穿戴产品，对你的生活有哪些变化？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-292eb9b1c6175e3223f83d923867b838_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653433721"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It7PDp621sbIoEAMaCTEwNzQ4NTM2MSC2q4ixBjAAOFVAHXIJNjUzNDMzNzIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1713875663.935856", "card_id": "Q_653473953", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何在职场中处理同事间的八卦和流言蜚语？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5928e83b3ebab90147e9d8d85cdd5f45_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653473953"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It7PDp621sbIoEAMaCTEwNzQ5NDM2NCD29ImxBjAAO